WEBVTT

00:02.000 --> 00:04.030
<i>Previously on</i> American Gothic...

00:04.054 --> 00:04.999
BRADY: The Silver Bells Killer.

00:05.024 --> 00:07.514
Consistent M.O.:
strangulation with a belt.

00:07.539 --> 00:08.773
Was found in the rubble.

00:08.798 --> 00:11.737
It is the first SBK murder
weapon ever recovered.

00:11.762 --> 00:13.329
We have to tell the truth.

00:14.097 --> 00:15.597
Just close your eyes.

00:15.599 --> 00:18.200
TESSA: <i>I can't bury our dad</i>
until I have some answers.

00:18.202 --> 00:20.736
MADELINE: <i>If you're looking</i>
for the bells, they're gone.

00:20.738 --> 00:23.155
TESSA: <i>When we were kids,
Garrett was the sweetest.</i>

00:23.180 --> 00:25.230
He was gonna marry Molly and have kids.

00:25.255 --> 00:27.839
- I'm sorry about Jack.
- He needs therapy.

00:28.074 --> 00:29.480
You had a dark streak, too.

00:30.315 --> 00:31.899
- I think you should leave.
- Why?

00:31.924 --> 00:33.145
Because you're a grenade.

00:33.147 --> 00:36.415
GARRETT: Then maybe you
should handle me <i>carefully.</i>

00:42.589 --> 00:44.389
♪

